project: Cirkl - Authentic Social Network
type: iOS Mobile App
language: Swift 5.9+
minimum_ios: 17.0
ui_framework: SwiftUI
architecture: MVVM + Clean Architecture
design: Glassmorphic (VisionOS inspired)

core_features:
  - Physical connection verification (QR/NFC/BLE)
  - AI-powered matching & orchestration  
  - Real-time presence detection
  - Zero fake profiles guarantee
  - Privacy by design

technical_rules:
  - ALWAYS use SwiftUI (no UIKit unless critical)
  - Use async/await for ALL async operations
  - SwiftData for local persistence
  - Dependency injection for testability
  - @MainActor for ALL UI updates
  - Proper error handling with Result type
  - Follow Swift API Design Guidelines

code_style:
  - Max 300 lines per file
  - Descriptive variable names
  - Comments for complex logic
  - Group related functionality
  - Use extensions for protocol conformance

when_asked_to_code:
  - Create reusable components
  - Include proper error handling
  - Add accessibility labels
  - Write unit tests for ViewModels
  - Implement smooth 60fps animations
  - Use SF Symbols for icons

context:
  company: Cirkl
  mission: "Connecting Authentically, Growing Intelligently"
  founders: Gil Benittah (CEO), Denis Gihan (CFO), Gilles Mamane (CTO)
  target: Israel POC → USA → Global
  key_metrics:
    - 67% organic connection rate
    - 0% fake profiles
    - 12.4k€ lifetime value
    - 1.7 viral coefficient